snippet.title: Gigantic - PAX East 2015 Trailer
snippet.description:
Heroes charge into the fray in this sneak peak at Gigantic, a team action game coming fall 2015 to Windows 10 and Xbox One.

Learn more at: http://www.gogigantic.com
Like: https://www.facebook.com/GoGigantic
Follow: https://twitter.com/GoGigantic
Watch: http://www.twitch.tv/gogigantic
